AttrSerializable
================

This plugin makes it easy to create a whitelist of attributes for your models that you want to be returned when using the to_xml and to_json attributes.


Example
=======

  class User < ActiveRecord::Base
    attr_serializable :login, :name
    ...
  end

  User.find(:first).to_xml # => "<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<user>\n  <login>joey</login>\n  <name>Joey Schoblaska</name>\n</user>\n"


